data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the charming Lake Carolina Subdivision! This picturesque Charleston-style residence offers a perfect blend of Southern elegance and modern comfort.  As you approach, you will be blown away by the home's curb appeal. Step onto the front porch and take in the tranquil views of the natural area across the street, adding a touch of serenity to your daily life. This home effortlessly combines indoor and outdoor living. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this home invites you into a spacious open floor plan with luxury vinyl tile floors, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for both everyday living and entertaining. The heart of this home is its large living room overlooking the natural area full of wildlife, birds and trees. In the galley-style kitchen, a culinary haven featuring sleek appliances, ample counter space, and stylish cabinetry, imagine preparing meals and creating memories. The side patio, accessible through the kitchen, offers a private retreat for outdoor gatherings or a quiet morning coffee. The thoughtful design of this Charleston-style residence ensures that every corner is utilized for both aesthetic appeal and functional living.This home in Lake Carolina Subdivision provides the perfect canvas for your lifestyle in the Midlands. Enjoy the modern amenities and comfort this residence offers as well as those of the HOA including access to the pool as well as tennis courts and Lake Carolina.
